This guide explains how to submit your work for the GenAI Awards. You can make your submission through the Marketplace, which accepts a variety of entries, including GenAI, Widget, and Vehicle App projects.
On the Marketplace website, we refer to a GenAI submission as a &ldquo;Package.&rdquo;
From previous Review your team screen. Click Go to marketplace, or you can go to https://marketplace.digital.auto In the marketplace, if you&rsquo;ve previously logged into the GenAI website, your login should carry over.
